v>With Darth half-boy and Palps.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OOXNuUS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Heartburn time, old man!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JL0Rmui.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>From young Luke to dead Luke, in order.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NSY1JUG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>With our boy, R2.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/K0a7by6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A Trooper I met while walking back from the store. He said "Hey, are you Fluke Skywalker? " Yep! Finally, I have people asking that vs. are you.  Mark Hamill? That is a good thing for both Mark and me.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2A94IYM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Not a cat tax but will a beef cake tax work? Tee hee. A fun shirt I brought to Anaheim. More pix from Disneyland tonight are heading your way, my Dudes. May the Force Be with you!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/rvB3o1A</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[imflukeskywalker]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Ted thinks he did something here.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/sq3BaUi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9b5FNc5.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/tedcruz/status/1530307396614103041?t=yOfQQbhANVmjGmkLyRRKTg&s=19</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/sq3BaUi</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[internetmexican]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fuck Ken Paxton #NRABloodmoney</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/pG84qJ1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NXysBl8.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div